{
  "texts": [
    "To mitigate this, a two-stage sampling strategy was implemented in the TXtreme model.",
    "In the first stage, random subsections of length L + H were sampled from the time series data, ensuring they did not overlap with Feedforward Neural Network (FFNN) [55]: FFNNs process information in one direction, making them simple for time series forecasting.",
    "They use past values as inputs to predict future ones but might struggle with complex dependencies and long-term patterns.DeepAR [56]: It is a deep learning model developed for probabilistic forecasting.",
    "It conditions predictions on the entire input time series, enabling it to capture complex patterns and provide uncertainty estimates, making it suitable for related time series forecasting.N-BEATS (\"Neural Basis Expansion Analysis for Time Series Forecasting\") [57]: N-BEATS decomposes time series into interpretable basis functions, which it combines for forecasting.",
    "Its stacks and blocks design allows hierarchical feature extraction, providing flexibility, scalability, and interpretability for various forecasting tasks.WaveNet [58]: WaveNet, originally for audio generation, is effective for autoregressive modeling in TSF."
  ]
}